        <div class = "container my-4">
            <h2>Games</h2>
            <p>
              AlgoLAB has a very interesting games playground section with many games designed using different algorithmic approaches.
            </p><br>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="card col-md-3 m-2">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h3>N Queen</h3>
                  <p>The N Queen is the problem of placing N chess queens on an NÃ—N chessboard so that no two queens attack each other.</p>
